::Slayer/Lavacons::

Slayer swears, swirling out of the way of the shots fired from 
Wheeljack. He turns around to fire more, knowing it was useless as 
every shot hit the shields and went no further.

A missile explodes against Slayer's back, sending the bot flipping 
forward. A loud battlecry behind him makes him turn around in time to 
see Recklessa flying down at him. The two bots collide in the air, 
flying down toward the water.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Astral flies into the battle, firing twenty shots at Prebon.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Fenox flies in behind her leader, firing several bolts at Blaze.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Starlight glides into the battle, firing three darts (with 
tranquilizer) at Bullet.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
Griplash flies/falls with stile into the scene, firing two missiles 
at Iguanus.
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
The Iron Fist's defences keep firing.
